      • BlastOptions

        public BlastOptions(int num_alignments,
                    double evalue,
                    int blast_threshold,
                    int window_size,
                    int word_size,
                    double best_hit_overhang,
                    double best_hit_score_edge,
                    int gapextend,
                    int gapopen,
                    boolean ungapped)
        The BlastOptions parameterized constructor
        Parameters:
        num_alignments - The alignments shown
        evalue - The expect value (E) for saving hits
        blast_threshold - The minimum score to add a word to the BLAST lookup table
        window_size - The multiple hits window size
        word_size - The word size of initial match
        best_hit_overhang - The Best Hit algorithm overhang value
        best_hit_score_edge - The Best Hit algorithm score edge value
        gapextend - The cost to extend a gap
        gapopen - The cost to open a gap
        ungapped - Whether to perform an ungapped alignment
